## **4. Test Coverage**

###  Positive Flow
- Create â†’ Retrieve â†’ Update â†’ Delete â†’ Verify Lifecycle  

### Negative & Edge Cases
The PetStore APIâ€¦ isnâ€™t perfect. Instead of hiding that, my framework captures it.

| **Scenario**        | **Expected REST** | **Actual API** | **Framework Expectation** |
|----------------------|------------------:|---------------:|--------------------------:|
| **Non existing ID**  | 404               | 404             |  404 handled gracefully |
| **Negative ID**      | 400 / 404         | 404             |  treated as 404         |
| **Empty JSON `{}`**  | 400               | 200             |  handled as 200         |
| **Missing fields**   | 400               | 200             |  handled as 200         |
| **Invalid payload**  | 400               | 200             |  handled as 200         |


