---

  ## **8. Key Design Choices**

 1. Gateway pattern-
All HTTP logic lives in PetGateway.
Test classes stay business-focused and readable.

2. Data factory-
PetBlueprint dynamically creates valid/invalid payloads.
Tests stay DRY, expressive, and maintainable.

3. Reusable assertions-
Consistent validation logic, centralized and extendable.

4. Readable tests-
Each test reads like behavior documentation, not just checks.

5. Real-world behavior-
This framework doesnâ€™t fake the APIâ€™s oddities â€” it reflects them.
